---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Catalyst Neuromorphic" description="The path to superintelligence isn't scaling the wrong architecture. It's building the right one." hasFog={true}>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="v7-hero" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v7-hero-inner">
      <p class="v7-label reveal">About</p>
      <h1 class="v7-hero-h1 reveal">AI has a hardware problem.</h1>
      <p class="v7-hero-sub reveal">We're building the processors to fix it.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 1: The scaling wall (heading + image left, text right) -->
  <section class="v7-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v7-wide">
      <div class="v7-two-col reveal">
        <div class="v7-col-heading">
          <h2 class="v7-h2">The scaling wall</h2>
          <div class="v7-col-img-wrap">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558980532-a08d3f00d59a?w=800&q=80&auto=format"
              alt="Rows of servers in a data centre bathed in blue light"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
              class="v7-col-img"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="v7-col-text">
          <div class="v7-prose">
            <p>Modern AI runs on hardware that was never designed for intelligence. GPUs burn hundreds of watts per chip. Data centres already consume over 2% of global electricity, and that share is climbing fast. Training a single large language model can use more energy than a hundred homes do in a year. The models are getting bigger, but the returns are shrinking.</p>
            <p>And for all that power, these systems still can't learn from new information without being retrained from scratch. They can't run without a data centre. They can't operate without sending your data to someone else's infrastructure.</p>
            <p>The path to true superintelligence isn't throwing more power at the wrong architecture. Nature spent millions of years perfecting the most efficient computational system ever created &mdash; the brain. 20 watts. Continuous learning. Real-time processing. No cloud required. The gap between current AI and real intelligence isn't a software problem. It's a hardware problem.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="v7-rule" style="position:relative;z-index:1;"></div>

  <!-- SECTION 2: Neuromorphic processors (text left, heading + image right — REVERSED) -->
  <section class="v7-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v7-wide">
      <div class="v7-two-col v7-two-col--reverse reveal">
        <div class="v7-col-text">
          <div class="v7-prose">
            <p>Neuromorphic chips compute the way neurons do. They're event-driven &mdash; they only consume energy when there's something to process. They can learn on the hardware itself, not just run pre-trained models. They operate at the edge, on-device, without cloud dependency. And they do it at a fraction of the power cost.</p>
            <p>This technology exists. Intel has Loihi. IBM built TrueNorth. But both are closed, corporate, and inaccessible. If you're not inside those companies or their select research programmes, you don't get access. The hardware that could reshape computing is locked behind walls.</p>
            <p>Catalyst is building the open alternative. Full processor designs, published research, and a cloud platform anyone can use today. We're not asking for permission to compete with billion-dollar companies. We're just doing it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="v7-col-heading">
          <h2 class="v7-h2">Neuromorphic processors.</h2>
          <div class="v7-col-img-wrap">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1647356191320-d7a1f80ca777?w=800&q=80&auto=format"
              alt="Abstract neural pathways rendered in blue and violet light"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
              class="v7-col-img"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="v7-rule" style="position:relative;z-index:1;"></div>

  <!-- SECTION 3: Where we are (heading + image left, text right) -->
  <section class="v7-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v7-wide">
      <div class="v7-two-col reveal">
        <div class="v7-col-heading">
          <h2 class="v7-h2">Where we are.</h2>
          <div class="v7-col-img-wrap">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1598406444638-d4e842c982ab?w=800&q=80&auto=format"
              alt="Macro photograph of a silicon wafer showing individual chip dies"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
              class="v7-col-img"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="v7-col-text">
          <div class="v7-prose">
            <p>Two processor generations designed, built in software, and validated on real FPGA hardware. Both backed by published research you can read today. A live cloud API &mdash; run a neuromorphic network from your terminal, right now, without buying anything.</p>
            <p>We're raising funding and building toward manufactured silicon. The architecture is complete, tested, and protected by patent. A physical chip you can hold, running real neuromorphic intelligence &mdash; that's what we're moving toward.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="v7-rule" style="position:relative;z-index:1;"></div>

  <!-- SECTION 4: Founder (text left, heading right — REVERSED) -->
  <section class="v7-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v7-wide">
      <div class="v7-two-col v7-two-col--reverse reveal">
        <div class="v7-col-text">
          <div class="v7-prose">
            <p><strong class="v7-strong">Henry Shulayev Barnes</strong> &mdash; engineering student at the University of Aberdeen. Started Catalyst because the neuromorphic hardware that should exist doesn't, and the hardware that does exist isn't accessible. Currently a member of Techscaler, Scotland's tech startup community.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="v7-col-heading">
          <h2 class="v7-h2">Founder.</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="v7-rule" style="position:relative;z-index:1;"></div>

  <!-- TRUST: 1x4 row with top borders -->
  <section class="v7-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v7-wide">
      <h2 class="v7-h2 reveal" style="margin-bottom:48px;">Don't take our word for it.</h2>
      <div class="v7-trust-row reveal-stagger">
        <div class="v7-trust-item">
          <h3 class="v7-trust-title">Read the papers</h3>
          <p class="v7-trust-desc">Published on Zenodo with DOIs. Open access. Every claim documented and peer-reviewable.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="v7-trust-item">
          <h3 class="v7-trust-title">Try the cloud</h3>
          <p class="v7-trust-desc">The API is live. Run a neuromorphic network from your terminal. Free tier available.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="v7-trust-item">
          <h3 class="v7-trust-title">Check the hardware</h3>
          <p class="v7-trust-desc">Our designs run on real FPGA boards, not just simulators. Physical hardware execution.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="v7-trust-item">
          <h3 class="v7-trust-title">Join the community</h3>
          <p class="v7-trust-desc">Open GitHub, public research, growing backers. We build in the open.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- IP: inline pairs with middots -->
  <section class="v7-section-compact" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v7-wide">
      <div class="v7-ip reveal">
        <span class="v7-ip-item"><span class="v7-ip-label">UK Patents</span> Filed Feb 2026</span>
        <span class="v7-ip-sep">&middot;</span>
        <span class="v7-ip-item"><span class="v7-ip-label">RTL</span> BSL 1.1 &mdash; proprietary</span>
        <span class="v7-ip-sep">&middot;</span>
        <span class="v7-ip-item"><span class="v7-ip-label">SDK</span> BSL 1.1</span>
        <span class="v7-ip-sep">&middot;</span>
        <span class="v7-ip-item"><span class="v7-ip-label">Papers</span> Open access Zenodo</span>
        <span class="v7-ip-sep">&middot;</span>
        <span class="v7-ip-item"><span class="v7-ip-label">API Client</span> MIT &mdash; open source</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- GET IN TOUCH -->
  <section class="connect-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <h2 style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-size:clamp(2.4rem,5vw,3.6rem); font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.035em; line-height:1.08; text-align:center; margin-bottom:18px;">Get in touch.</h2>
    <p class="connect-email"><a href="mailto:henry@catalyst-neuromorphic.com">henry@catalyst-neuromorphic.com</a></p>
    <div class="connect-grid">
      <a href="https://github.com/catalyst-neuromorphic" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="connect-card"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M15 22v-4a4.8 4.8 0 0 0-1-3.5c3 0 6-2 6-5.5.08-1.25-.27-2.48-1-3.5.28-1.15.28-2.35 0-3.5 0 0-1 0-3 1.5-2.64-.5-5.36-.5-8 0C6 2 5 2 5 2c-.3 1.15-.3 2.35 0 3.5A5.4 5.4 0 0 0 4 9c0 3.5 3 5.5 6 5.5-.39.49-.68 1.05-.85 1.65S8.93 17.38 9 18v4"/><path d="M9 18c-4.51 2-5-2-7-2"/></svg><span class="connect-label">GitHub</span><span class="connect-sub">Source &amp; contributions</span></a>
      <a href="/research" class="connect-card"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg><span class="connect-label">Research</span><span class="connect-sub">Papers &amp; benchmarks</span></a>
      <a href="https://ko-fi.com/catalystneuromorphic" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="connect-card"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg><span class="connect-label">Support</span><span class="connect-sub">Buy us a coffee on Ko-Fi</span></a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style is:global>
    /* =============================================
       V7 — Two-Column Editorial (Resend/Graphcore)
       with integrated photography
       ============================================= */

    /* Hero */
    .v7-hero {
      padding: 180px 32px 100px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .v7-hero-inner {
      max-width: 960px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .v7-label {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.7);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .v7-hero-h1 {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      line-height: 1.05;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .v7-hero-sub {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.3rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
      margin-top: 24px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Wide container */
    .v7-wide {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 32px;
    }

    /* Sections */
    .v7-section {
      padding: 100px 0;
    }
    .v7-section-compact {
      padding: 40px 0 80px;
    }

    /* Horizontal rule */
    .v7-rule {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 32px;
      height: 0;
    }
    .v7-rule::after {
      content: '';
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      height: 1px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    }

    /* Section headings */
    .v7-h2 {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      line-height: 1.1;
      color: #fff;
      margin: 0 0 24px 0;
    }

    /* Two-column layout */
    .v7-two-col {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 38% 1fr;
      gap: 60px;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .v7-two-col--reverse {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 38%;
    }

    .v7-col-heading {
      position: sticky;
      top: 120px;
    }
    .v7-col-text {
      /* text column */
    }

    /* Column images */
    .v7-col-img-wrap {
      margin-top: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }
    .v7-col-img {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
      filter: brightness(0.65) saturate(1.15);
      transition: filter 0.6s ease;
    }
    .v7-col-img-wrap:hover .v7-col-img {
      filter: brightness(0.8) saturate(1.3);
    }

    /* Prose */
    .v7-prose p {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.4vw, 1.08rem);
      line-height: 1.85;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .v7-prose p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .v7-strong {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* Trust: 1x4 row */
    .v7-trust-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 32px;
    }
    .v7-trust-item {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      padding-top: 24px;
    }
    .v7-trust-title {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .v7-trust-desc {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
    }

    /* IP inline */
    .v7-ip {
      text-align: center;
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      line-height: 2.2;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    }
    .v7-ip-label {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .v7-ip-sep {
      margin: 0 14px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .v7-hero {
        padding: 140px 24px 60px;
      }
      .v7-section {
        padding: 64px 0;
      }
      .v7-wide {
        padding: 0 24px;
      }

      /* Collapse to single column */
      .v7-two-col,
      .v7-two-col--reverse {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 24px;
      }

      /* Heading always first on mobile */
      .v7-two-col--reverse .v7-col-heading {
        order: -1;
      }
      .v7-two-col--reverse .v7-col-text {
        order: 0;
      }

      .v7-col-heading {
        position: static;
      }

      .v7-col-img-wrap {
        margin-top: 16px;
      }
      .v7-col-img {
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
      }

      /* Trust: 2 col then 1 col */
      .v7-trust-row {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 24px;
      }

      /* IP: stack */
      .v7-ip-sep {
        display: none;
      }
      .v7-ip-item {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .v7-trust-row {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    /* Connect section */
    .connect-section{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px 32px 100px}.connect-email{font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(1.4rem,3vw,2.2rem);font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-0.02em;text-align:center;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:56px}.connect-email a{color:rgba(59,130,246,0.8);text-decoration:none;transition:color 0.3s}.connect-email a:hover{color:#60A5FA}.connect-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px}.connect-card{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;text-align:center;padding:36px 24px;border-radius:20px;text-decoration:none;color:#fff;background:linear-gradient(165deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.12) 0%,rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 35%,rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 100%);backdrop-filter:blur(28px) saturate(190%) brightness(1.06);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(28px) saturate(190%) brightness(1.06);border:1px solid transparent;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.45),inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.14),inset 0 -1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.02);position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:box-shadow 0.5s,transform 0.3s}.connect-card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 12px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.55),inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.18),inset 0 -1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.03)}.connect-card::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;border-radius:20px;padding:1px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(59,130,246,0.22) 0%,rgba(59,130,246,0.06) 25%,rgba(59,130,246,0.02) 50%,rgba(59,130,246,0.06) 75%,rgba(59,130,246,0.18) 100%);-webkit-mask:linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box,linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);-webkit-mask-composite:xor;mask-composite:exclude;pointer-events:none;z-index:5;opacity:0.55;transition:opacity 0.4s}.connect-card:hover::before{opacity:1}.connect-card svg{color:#60A5FA;margin-bottom:16px;position:relative;z-index:2}.connect-label{font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:6px;position:relative;z-index:2}.connect-sub{font-size:0.78rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);position:relative;z-index:2}@media(max-width:640px){.connect-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  </style>

</BaseLayout>
